        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:2:3:130:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/130/1",
        "text": [
          " : «لاَ بَأْسَ أَنْ يَأْتِيَ اَلرَّجُلُ مَكَّةَ فَيَطُوفَ أَيَّامَ مِنًى وَ لاَ يَبِيتَ بِهَا»."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.3013 - Jamil narrated from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"There is no harm if a man goes to Mecca, performs Tawaf during the days of Mina, and does not stay overnight there.\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 1448,
        "local_index": 2,
        "narrator_chain": {
          "parts": [
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "3014 - وَ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "سَأَلَهُ لَيْثٌ اَلْمُرَادِيُّ :"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " عَنِ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "اَلرَّجُلِ يَأْتِي مَكَّةَ أَيَّامَ مِنًى بَعْدَ فَرَاغِهِ مِنْ زِيَارَةِ اَلْبَيْتِ فَيَطُوفُ بِالْبَيْتِ تَطَوُّعاً"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " فَقَالَ"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:2:3:130:2",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/130/2",
        "text": [
          " «اَلْمُقَامُ بِمِنًى أَحَبُّ إِلَيَّ »."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.3014 - Laith Al-Muradi asked Abu Abdullah (as) about a man who goes to Mecca during the days of Mina after completing the visitation of the House and performs Tawaf around the Kaaba voluntarily.\nImam (as) replied: \"Staying in Mina is more beloved to me.\""
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
